keystone.api.wrappers

Class BlockMask

  • java.lang.Object
    • keystone.api.wrappers.BlockMask

  • public class BlockMask
extends java.lang.Object
    A block mask for a filter. Used to restrict operations to either only a set of blocks or every block except a set of blocks
